alexcrichton opened PR #10843 from alexcrichton:move-wasi-http-tests to bytecodealliance:main:

This commit moves all existing wasi-http tests to a new p2 module. No actual tests are modified here, they're just moved around. This is to make room for a future p3 module with WASIp3-related tests.
